---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SEO from '../components/SEO.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import DisclaimerBanner from '../components/DisclaimerBanner.astro';
import StickyMobileBookingCTA from '../components/StickyMobileBookingCTA.astro';

const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Terms & Disclaimer', href: '/terms-and-disclaimer' }
];
---

<Layout title="Terms & Medical Disclaimer">
  <SEO
    title="Terms of Service & Medical Disclaimer"
    description="Important legal, ethical, and clinical service disclaimers regarding international online consultations."
  />
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
    <Breadcrumbs paths={breadcrumbs} />
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">Terms & Disclaimer</h1>
      <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-700 max-w-none">
        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8 border border-gray-300">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-0">Important Clinical Services Notice</h2>
          <p class="font-medium text-brand-navy">
            Rabbia Ashraf NeuroCare provides parent guidance, educational resources, developmental support planning, report review support, school guidance, and between-session parent support programs.
          </p>
          <p class="font-medium text-brand-navy mt-4">
            These services are not emergency services.
          </p>
          <p class="font-medium text-brand-navy mt-4">
            Online support does not replace local medical, psychological, educational, legal, crisis, or school-based services.
          </p>
          <p class="font-medium text-brand-navy mt-4">
            Between-session support programs are designed to support parent understanding, home carryover, routines, and practical implementation. They do not guarantee outcomes and do not replace direct therapy, diagnosis, emergency care, or local regulated services where required.
          </p>
          <p class="font-medium text-brand-navy mt-4">
            Regulated services are provided only within the professional scope, credentials, and legal requirements of the professional and client location.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-4 italic">
            Internal team note: Rabbia Ashraf NeuroCare may use internal support staff, consultants, collaborators, or administrative assistance for operations, resources, education support, and program delivery. Public booking, communication, and service coordination remain through Rabbia Ashraf NeuroCare.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">1. Nature of International Services</h2>
        <p>International support may include parent education, developmental guidance, ASD/ADHD support planning, behavior strategy discussion, executive-function routines, school communication preparation, resource guidance, and referral direction. Clinical therapy, diagnosis, assessment, and regulated psychological services are provided only where legally and ethically permitted by the professional's credentials and the client's location.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">2. Emergency Situations</h2>
        <p>Online parent consultation is not appropriate for emergency situations or acute crises. In the event of a medical or psychological emergency, please contact your local emergency services or proceed to the nearest hospital.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">3. Guarantees</h2>
        <p>While we use evidence-based strategies, behavioral outcomes depend on numerous factors. We cannot guarantee specific results. Between-session support programs are designed to support parent understanding, home carryover, routines, and practical implementation. They do not guarantee outcomes and do not replace direct therapy, diagnosis, emergency care, or local regulated services where required.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <StickyMobileBookingCTA />
</Layout>
